uses were damaged, some of them seriously.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.alertageo.org/2020/01/02/terremoto-magnitud-5-8-genera-danos-al-noreste-de-iran/|title=terremoto magnitud 5.8 genera da\u00f1os al noreste de Ir\u00e1n|last=Lopez|first=Rodrigo Contreras|date=2020-01-02|website=Alerta Geo|language=es|access-date=2020-01-02}}</ref>\n|<nowiki>-</nowiki>\n|<nowiki>-</nowiki>\n|-\n| 4<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/SismologicoMX/status/1213689858767540225|title=SISMO Magnitud 5.8 Loc  38 km al SURESTE de UNION HIDALGO, OAX 04/01/20 22:40:48 Lat 16.22 Lon -94.59 Pf 83 km|website=ssn.unam.mx|access-date=2020-01-05}}</ref>||{{flag|Mexico}}, [[Oaxaca]], 38 km southeast of [[Uni\u00f3n Hidalgo]]|| 5.8|| 83.0|| VII|| Minor damage to some homes. No loss of life was reported.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/sismo-en-oaxaca-reportan-danos-menores-por-sismo-de-magnitud-6|title=Reportan da\u00f1os menores por sismo de magnitud 6 en Oaxaca|last=|first=|date=2020-01-05|website=[[El Universal (Mexico City)|El Universal]]|language=es|access-date=2020-01-05}}</ref>|| -||-\n|-\n|6<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/eventpage/pr2020006006/executive|title = M 5.8 - 9km SSE of Indios, Puerto Rico|website=earthquake.usgs.gov|access-date=2020-01-06}}</ref>\n|{{flag|United States}}, [[Guayanilla, Puerto Rico|Puerto Rico, Guayanilla]] offshore, 9 km south southeast of [[Indios, Guayanilla, Puerto Rico|Indios]]\n|5.8\n|6.0\n|VI\n|Various houses were badly damaged, and power was cut in [[Guayanilla, Puerto Rico|Guayanilla municipality]]. Landslides also blocked roads.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.primerahora.com/noticias/puerto-rico/nota/impactantesdanosporelterremotode58alsurdepuertorico-1385417/|title=Impactantes da\u00f1os por el terremoto de 5.8 al sur de Puerto Rico|date=2020-01-06|website=Primera Hora|language=en|access-date=2020-01-06}}</ref>\n|<nowiki>-</nowiki>\n|<nowiki>-</nowiki>\n|-\n|7<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://earth